data.description:
NEW carpet installation. This property is nestled in the sought-after neighborhood of Surprise Farms! You'll be immediately captivated by the spacious family room that effortlessly flows into the chef's gourmet kitchen. The kitchen boasts gorgeous cabinets, granite countertops, a convenient island, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making it a dream come true for any culinary enthusiast.
Adjacent to the kitchen is an elegant dining area, complete with a slider that opens up to the backyard featuring easy care artificial grass. The master suite is nothing short of extraordinary! In addition to all these incredible features, this property also has a bonus room, perfect for hosting gatherings.
